Para criar a imagem de capa do podcast, utilizei o seguinte prompt no Leonardo IA:

"create a female mathematician teacher character as podcaster with microphone, using tecnology in education,
schools' elements, mug of coffe, retro style, isometric, game style, down angle , game boy colors, 
8 bits, retro sprites --ar 1:1 --v 5.2"

A imagem pode ser acessada em https://github.com/marillia2002/project_dio_podcast/blob/main/podcast_project_image%20(2).jpg
